Description: Bibliographic data from around 900-000 articles published by Nature Publishing Group (NPG) from 1845 through to the present day. Additionally the datasets include NPG products and subjects ontologies. Datasets include:* [npg:Article](npg-articles)* [npg:Catalog](npg-catalogs)* [npg:Citation](npg-citations)* [npg:Contributor](npg-contributors)* [npg:Coverage](npg-coverages)* [npg:DataCitation](npg-data-citations)* [npg:Graph](npg-graphs)* [npg:Product](npg-products)* [npg:Publication](npg-publications)* [npg:Subject](npg-subjects)* [npg:Technique](npg-techniques)* [npg:Term](npg-terms)Class and property URIs in the [npg:](http://ns.nature.com/terms/) namespace are not dereferenceable.
